          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0583P0-00915'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_64' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        4.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0583P0-00916'>
        <a name='S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_65'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alfred-dubs' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_65' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alfred Dubs' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alfred-dubs" title="Mr Alfred Dubs">Lord Dubs</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The commission, as I said earlier, has no powers to ban parades. A determination would be largely a matter of indicating the particular route that a
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_20gc' title='Col. 20GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 November 1997 vol 583 c20GC' name='column_20gc' href='#column_20gc' rel='bookmark'>20GC</a>
