      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0583P0-00970'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_119' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        5.45 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0583P0-00971'>
        <a name='S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_120'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-richard-holme' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_120' title='Link to this speech by Mr Richard Holme' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
