      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0583P0-01002'>
        <a name='S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_151'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-alderdice' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0583P0_19971112_GCR_151' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Alderdice' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
